      "widgets_values": [
        "guide_size建議在512~1024範圍之間，數字越大速度越慢。如果面部修復功能沒有生效時，需提高guide_size的數字。\n\nsteps:2~8，步數越多越面部修復越仔細，但速度會更慢。\n\n調整\"denoise\"可以控制面部重繪的幅度。\n\n調整bbox_threshold, bbox_dolation, sam_diation 的數值可以控制蒙版尺寸，建議0~50之間。\n\nThe guide size is recommended to be between 512 and 1024; the larger the number, the slower the speed.\nIf the facial repair function is ineffective, the guide_size number needs to be increased.\n\nSteps: 2~8. The more steps, the more detailed the facial retouching, but the slower the process.\n\nAdjusting \"denoise\" controls the extent of facial redrawing.\n\nAdjusting the values ​​of bbox_threshold, bbox_dolation, and sam_diation can control the mask size; a range of 0 to 50 is recommended."
      ],
